},
ja={
{
name={"里奈"},
"「単に疎ましかっただけ……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00146",
linknext="block_00148",
},
block_00148={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rna_001703",ch="rna"},
},
ja={
{
name={"里奈"},
"「うらやましかっただけ……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00147",
linknext="block_00149",
},
block_00149={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rna_001704",ch="rna"},
},
ja={
{
name={"里奈"},
"「日陰にいる毒きのこの少女には、いつもオオカミは輝いて見えた」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00148",
linknext="block_00150",
},
block_00150={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rna_001705",ch="rna"},
},
ja={
{
name={"里奈"},
"「青く黒いたてがみ、白く輝く肌」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00149",
linknext="block_00151",
},
block_00151={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rna_001706",ch="rna"},
},
ja={
{
name={"里奈"},
"「そのすべてが美しく、そして疎ましかった……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00150",
linknext="block_00152",
},
block_00152={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rna_001707",ch="rna"},
},
ja={
{
name={"里奈"},
"「死の淵にいる私にとって……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00151",
linknext="block_00153",
},
block_00153={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rna_001708",ch="rna"},
},
ja={
{
name={"里奈"},
"「だから……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00152",
linknext="block_00154",
},
block_00154={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
"ごめんね。優美。",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00153",
linknext="block_00155",
},
block_00155={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
"あなたの牙を抜いてしまったのは私。",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00154",
linknext="block_00156",
},
block_00156={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
"あなたの速い足を奪ってしまったのは私。",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00155",
linknext="block_00157",
},
block_00157={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
"あなたを普通の少女にしてしまったのは私。",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00156",
linknext="block_00158",
},
block_00158={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rna_001709",ch="rna"},
},
ja={
{
name={"里奈"},
"「だから、私は最後まであなたのそばにいるよ……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00157",
linknext="block_00159",
},
