text={
vo={
{"vo",file="fem_rna_001711",ch="rna"},
},
ja={
{
name={"里奈"},
"「今のは……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00165",
linknext="block_00167",
},
block_00167={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
"今のは何だろう？",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00166",
linknext="block_00168",
},
block_00168={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
"今、私に優美の声で聞こえたのは、たしかにグリム版の赤ずきん。",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00167",
linknext="block_00169",
},
block_00169={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
"その結末はペロー版とは大いに違う。",
